The Telegraph - Calcutta : Bengal
 Monday, December 16, 2002 				 Marriage mart in city
 A STAFF REPORTER																								Calcutta, Dec. 15: A city-based marriage-management agency will arrange a selection ceremony of prospective brides and grooms on December 22. 																								About 500 men and women would select life partners in the presence of their parents at a city hotel that day. 																								A show on national integration and an awareness drive on the importance of taking tests related to thalassaemia and other transmittable diseases for a healthy married life would be part of the show.
